eu.amidst.core.variables.stateSpaceTypes

Class FiniteStateSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.variables.StateSpaceType
      • eu.amidst.core.variables.stateSpaceTypes.FiniteStateSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<String>

    public class FiniteStateSpace
extends StateSpaceType
implements Iterable<String>
    This class extends the abstract class StateSpaceType and implements the interface Iterable<String>. It defines and handles the state space for discrete variables, i.e., the finite state space.
    See Also:
